Decompress Dectris bitshuffle lz4 data directly to indices/value arrays.


After git clone:

    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    python3 -m pip install .

To run it at ESRF:

    cd test
    python3 test_vs_hdf5plugin.py
    python3 bench1.py

